headline: Is Prologis (PLD) Starting To Look Expensive After Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Gains?
summary: If you are wondering whether Prologis at around US$129 per share looks like value or just a price you have to accept for quality, this breakdown is designed for you. The stock is up 0.3% over the past week, is broadly flat over the last month with a 0.2% decline, and has returned 0.3% year to date and 29.4% over the past year, alongside 16.7% over three years and 52.4% over five years.
